{"words":[{"word":"chunkie","count":6},{"word":"dark","count":6},{"word":"tide","count":6},{"word":"old","count":3},{"word":"camp","count":3},{"word":"children","count":3},{"word":"protect","count":2},{"word":"helmet","count":2},{"word":"teeny","count":2},{"word":"ones","count":2},{"word":"young","count":2},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"stronger","count":1},{"word":"feather","count":1},{"word":"struck","count":1},{"word":"former","count":1},{"word":"gladiator","count":1},{"word":"stayed","count":1},{"word":"behind","count":1},{"word":"cover","count":1},{"word":"everyone's","count":1},{"word":"retreat","count":1},{"word":"stood","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"glorious","count":1},{"word":"hunt","count":1},{"word":"little","count":1},{"word":"hunted","count":1},{"word":"end","count":1},{"word":"corruption","count":1},{"word":"crawled","count":1},{"word":"charged","count":1},{"word":"save","count":1},{"word":"knocking","count":1},{"word":"aside","count":1},{"word":"tainted","count":1},{"word":"helm","count":1},{"word":"pushing","count":1},{"word":"harm's","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"instead","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"moment","count":1},{"word":"warrior","count":1},{"word":"shames","count":1},{"word":"ask","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"turn","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"ravages","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"path","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"innocent","count":1},{"word":"lives","count":1},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"mad","count":1},{"word":"turned","count":1},{"word":"upside","count":1},{"word":"claw","count":1},{"word":"marks","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"friends","count":1},{"word":"fallen","count":1},{"word":"missing","count":1},{"word":"lift","count":1},{"word":"sword","count":1},{"word":"injuries","count":1},{"word":"sometimes","count":1},{"word":"hate","count":1},{"word":"bones","count":1},{"word":"mine","count":1},{"word":"whether","count":1},{"word":"weight","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"useless","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"courage","count":1},{"word":"fainted","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"running","count":1},{"word":"toward","count":1},{"word":"iron","count":1},{"word":"gates","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Chunkie... I'm sorry. I couldn't protect you from the Dark Tide... If only I'd been stronger...","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"This feather... It's from my old helmet.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"When the Dark Tide struck our old camp, as a former Gladiator, I stayed behind to cover everyone's retreat. Chunkie and Teeny also stood with me.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"We thought it would be a glorious hunt, but little did we know, we were the ones being hunted by the Dark Tide.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"In the end, as the corruption crawled up my helmet, it was Chunkie who charged to save me, knocking aside the tainted helm and pushing me out of harm's way.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"But Chunkie...","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"Chunkie let the Dark Tide take it instead... To protect me and Teeny...","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"...","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"Yes, Chunkie. Let's all go home now.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"Hold a moment, young warrior...","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"It shames me to ask this of you, but… I don't know who else to turn to.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"Could you help me find my children?","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"The Dark Tide ravages everything in its path. So many innocent lives lost. And the ones who went mad turned the camp upside down.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"See the claw marks around camp? My friends, fallen. My children, missing. And I... I can't lift a sword with these injuries.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"Sometimes I hate these old bones of mine... I don't even know whether it's the Dark Tide or just the weight of years that's made me this useless.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"Thank you. Young people like you always have such courage.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000},{"text":"Before I fainted, I last saw my children running toward the iron gates.","quest_name":"May Applause Greet You","quest_id":176750000}]}